---
title: Cal Smart Spiced Turkey Salad with Dill Pickle Cream
description: Looking for a salad with something a little extra? This dish nails it with a dollop of tangy dill pickle and onion cream. Don't throw out the pickle juice! It's used in the vinaigrette for an acidic kick!

